;;; Information
Full name:   malotru
Short name:  malotru
Description: A relatively comfortable Vim colorscheme primarily designed for 16color terminal emulators.
Author:      Romain Lafourcade <romainlafourcade@gmail.com>
Website:     https://github.com/romainl
License:     Same as Vim

Variant:     gui 256 16
Background:  dark

